name: Wellnesia
description: Wellnesia is an online gateway to all
overview:
Welcome to Wellnesia.com – an online gateway to all wellness and beauty treatments, therapists and topics. Our site is dedicated to helping wellness seekers search and conduct free online reservations across a broad listing of spas, beauty salons, fitness centers and lifestyle retreats. Wellnesia offers access to expert advice as well as interactive forums discussing main trends and treatments in wellness and beauty. In addition, the site features attractive deals specifically targeted to wellness and beauty enthusiasts.

Wellnesia is synonymous of wellness. We are passionate about wellness and are dedicated to bring wellness consumers, venues and therapists into one platform that delivers the ultimate online wellness experience.
